00:44:54.750 --> 00:44:56.705
We just buy everything there is.

00:44:56.705 --> 00:44:58.080
So I'd encourage
you to look here

00:44:58.080 --> 00:45:00.750
if you want to see more
details on how this works

00:45:00.750 --> 00:45:02.450
and why it works.

00:45:02.450 --> 00:45:06.140
So because it's exactly
