00:48:24.717 --> 00:48:26.342
What would you do
with the other three?

00:48:26.342 --> 00:48:27.580
AUDIENCE: Eat the gamma.

00:48:27.580 --> 00:48:29.872
MICHAEL SHORT: Eat the gamma
because most of the gammas

00:48:29.872 --> 00:48:32.590
